info.name: 6/1 A New Tab +8
info.description:
Now You Can Have A Picture On Your New Tab Button.
When You Open More Than 6 Or 8 Tabs, You'll See A Damn Cross, And No Picture.
Now You Can Open More Than 100 Tabs (I Opened 189) And The Picture Didn't Go Away.
info.additionalInfo:
A New Tab With Some Stuff.
Like: On Hover, It Stretch, You Can Change The Picture And Color.
